Rating: 4
I love this cake but the recipe has some omissions in it. First it doesn't tell you how much greek yogurt to use and second it doesn't tell you when to put the milk into the recipe. This could be why there are negative reviews of this cake. I used 8 ounces of greek yogurt and 1/2 c. of milk and it work great. I added both of these ingredients at the end of the recipe. I also used a tube pan and cooked it for 40 minutes. The cake was very moist and delicious.

