I baked this a little longer than the estimated time, about 55-60 minutes. I also added more butter and greek yogurt, came out perfectly moist. with this recipe I've noticed you can pretty much eyeball the amounts of sugar and yogurt, as the original recipe is sweet, but not sweet enough for my liking. this coffee cake is excellent. I have it for breakfast alongside my coffee, fruit and an egg. I hope you all enjoy it as well!

