Rating: 3
I don't see why people hated this so much. I used a 9 inch round cake pan, it cooked for the exact time it said, no sinking, and came out great. The streusel part was probably my favorite, could have eaten the whole bowl before I put it in the cake! I had to drain my yogurt, and did it overnight, but it only really needs about an hour and a bit to get all the excess water out.

